    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomime domini salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi. <persName
                            key="#Princeps #childOf" ref="#people/3010">Riccardus</persName>, divina
                        ordinante clementia Capuanorum <rs key="#Princeps">princeps</rs>, petitioni
                        sui dilecti <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#people/3016">Guarini</persName>,
                            <rs key="#Abbots">abbatis</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/3000" key="#Monasteries">S.
                            Laurentii</orgName>, clementer favet. Ego Riccardus, Dei gratia
                        Capuanorum princeps, <rs key="#childOf">filius</rs>
                        <persName key="#Princeps" ref="#people/3002">Iordani</persName>
                        <rs key="#Princeps">principis</rs>, dono et concedo, consilio magistrorum
                        meorum, scilicet <persName key="#Witness #uncle/auntOf" ref="#people/3015"
                            >Ionathae</persName>, <rs key="#uncle/auntOf">patrui</rs> mei, et
                            <persName key="#Witness #Count #cousinOf" ref="#people/2422"
                            >Roberti</persName>
                        <rs key="#Count">comitis</rs>, <rs key="#cousinOf">consobrini</rs> mei, et
                        aliorum baronum meorum, quorum nomina subscripta sunt, <rs
                            key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs> S. Laurentii , siti iuxta <placeName
                            key="#Cities" ref="#places/4000">Aversam</placeName>, et tibi domino
                        Guarino, abbati eiusdem monasterii, et successoribus tuis, in perpetuum, <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Ports"
                            >portum</rs> videlicet <rs
                            key="#Natural_landscape #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >fucis</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Natural_landscape #Ports" ref="#places/701"
                            >Patriae</placeName>, et totum <rs
                            key="#Sea #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >mare</rs>, a <placeName
                            key="#Shores #Sea #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            ref="#places/4062">Castello scilicet maris</placeName> usque <placeName
                            ref="#places/2356"
                            key="#Shores #Sea #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            >Cumam</placeName>, cum <rs
                            key="#Shores #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >plagia</rs> sua, in integrum, sicut in hora tempestatis suae aqua
                        decurrit, quaemadmodum pater meus possedit et dominatus est, ad praedictum
                        monasterium perpetuam proprietatem et possessionem, ut tu qui supra donne
                        Guarine abbas, tuique successores, et monachi ipsius monasterii liberam
                        potestatem habeatis dare securitatem in ipso praedicto portu fucis, et in
                        ipso mari, et in plagia ipsius maris, per omnia loca, a Castello maris usque
                        Cumam,omnibus naufragium pertinentibus, vel tempestatem maris fugientibus,
                        et omnibus ingredientibus et egredientibus, causa negotiandi sive piscandi,
                        sine inquietudine et molestatione alicuius altae vel humilis personae. Do
                        etiam et concedo, per hoc principale scriptum in perpetuum, prefato
                        monasterio Sancti Laurentii, ut tibi domino Guarino abbati, tuisque
                        successoribus, et monachis ipsius monasterii libere et sine
                            contradictione<rs key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"> liceat
                            per totum ipsum mare piscare</rs>, et piscatores in eo ponere, a
                        predicto Castello maris usque Cumam et <placeName
                            key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters" ref="#places/4081">Isclam
                            maiorem</placeName>, ita ut ullus piscare audeat iuxta hos terminos,
                        absque licentia abbatis, vel <rs key="#Monks">monachorum</rs> S. Laurentii,
                        siti iuxta Aversam, remota omni molestia et contrarietate mortalium omnium.
                        Quod si quis, diabolica suasione compulsus, hoc scriptum violare irritumve
                        facere presumpserit,<rs key="#Penalty"> centum auri optimi libras</rs>
                        persolvat, medietatem nostro palatio, medietatem praefatae ecclesiae. Et ut
                        scriptum firmum et inviolabile maneat in perpetuum, et ut firmius credatur
                        et diligentius ab omnibus observetur, manu nostra subscripsimus, et nostro
                        sigillo fecimus sigillari. Signum domini Riccardi (M) gloriosi principis. +
                        Ego <persName key="#Witness #Count #cousinOf" ref="#people/2422"
                            >Robertus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Count">comes</rs>. + Ego <persName key="#Witness #uncle/auntOf"
                            ref="#people/3015">Ionathas</persName>. Ex iussione praefate
                        serenissimae potestatis, scripsi ego <persName key="#Writer #Judge"
                            ref="#people/3012">Quiriacus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs>, in anno ipsius domini Riccardi decimo gloriosi
                        principis. Datum. xv. kalendas aprilis, anno ab incarnatione domini nostri
                        Iesu Christi .MXCI Scriptum in <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/4000"
                            >Aversa</placeName>, per. XIV. indictionem. + <persName key="#Witness"
                            ref="#people/3076">Guillielmus de Pirolo</persName>. + <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Thomas">Thomas</name></persName>. + <persName
                            key="#Witness" ref="#people/3079">Rainaldus Musca.</persName> +
                            <persName ref="#people/3080" key="#Witness">Rainaldus
                            Lapitius</persName>. + <persName key="#Witness" ref="#people/3077"
                            >Robertus de Ponte Indulfi</persName>. + <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Wido de Doeli">Guidone de Doeli</name></persName>. + <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Radulfus de Miczegros">Radulfus de
                                Miczegros</name></persName>. + <persName key="#Witness #Viscount"
                            ref="#people/3078">Stantione</persName>
                        <rs key="#Viscount">vicecomes</rs>.</ab>
                </div>
